I get two kids without the stretch marks.

198
00:09:01,970 --> 00:09:05,290
当我提到可能参选时  这就不再是玩笑话了
And when I mentioned I might run, it stopped becoming a joke.

199
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:07,530
艾伦能接受吗
Is Alan open to it?

200
00:09:08,640 --> 00:09:11,140
