- It was his idea. - And what about you?

201
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:13,750
我们深爱彼此
We do love each other.

202
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:15,700
他看上去是个好人
He seems like a good guy.

203
00:09:15,700 --> 00:09:18,970
是的  他的孩子也很棒
He is. And his children are wonderful.

204
00:09:21,150 --> 00:09:22,820
你也应该考虑结婚
You should think about getting hitched.

205
00:09:26,390 --> 00:09:27,700
我们要谈谈时间表吗
Should we talk timeline?

206
00:09:28,230 --> 00:09:30,880
-结婚的吗  -竞选
- For marriage? - The campaign.

207
00:09:43,860 --> 00:09:46,870
这可不是提议  这是会谈
This is far from an offer. This is a conversation.

208
00:09:46,870 --> 00:09:49,200
