That's way below what I'm worth. Even in this state.

216
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:08,400
你觉得多少合适
What do you think's appropriate?

217
00:10:08,430 --> 00:10:10,560
25万加上3%的广告投入
Two-fifty and three points on the ad-buy.

218
00:10:10,560 --> 00:10:13,340
-我们负担不起  -不  你们担得起
- That's beyond our means. - No, it's not.

219
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,370
这只是你财产的九牛一毛
It's a drop in the bucket from your estate.

220
00:10:15,370 --> 00:10:19,060
你说你想参加是因为你对这次竞选有信心
You said you wanted in because you believed in this campaign.

221
00:10:19,450 --> 00:10:22,120
-没错  -现在看来你是为了钱
- That's right. - Sounds like it's more about money.

222
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:26,000
我希望被重视  25万和少量广告投入并不多
It's about being valued. Two-fifty and the points is a bargain.

223
00:10:26,610 --> 00:10:29,370
我想为你工作  而不是向你乞讨
I want to work for you, just not as a beggar.

224
00:10:29,370 --> 00:10:31,230
我们还不信任你  道格
We don't trust you yet, Doug.

225
00:10:31,610 --> 00:10:35,080
可以说根本不信任你  所以你就是在乞讨
We don't even halfway trust you, so you are a beggar.

226
00:10:35,080 --> 00:10:38,990
我还没证明自己  你也不应该信任我
And you shouldn't trust me... until I prove myself.

227
00:10:39,540 --> 00:10:40,630
你不拿出筹码
That's a gamble you don't get to take

228
00:10:40,630 --> 00:10:42,370
就不能冒这个险
without putting chips on the table.

229
00:10:44,430 --> 00:10:46,140
我和会辛西娅谈的
Cynthia and I will discuss.

230
00:10:50,640 --> 00:10:51,770
感谢你抽空
Thank you for your time.

231
00:10:57,900 --> 00:10:59,070
我先看下外面
Let me check first.

232
00:11:02,050 --> 00:11:03,190
好了  安全
Okay, it's clear.

233
00:11:07,760 --> 00:11:10,150
-你怎么看  -为什么要冒险
- What do you think? - Why take the gamble?

234
00:11:10,460 --> 00:11:12,070
我不想一开始决策
I don't want us to start making decisions

235
00:11:12,070 --> 00:11:14,410
就处于劣势  只会吃亏
from a position of weakness. That is how you lose.

236
00:11:14,410 --> 00:11:16,940
我觉得这是引狼入室
I think we're inviting the fox into the hen house.

237
00:11:16,940 --> 00:11:18,220
要是间谍会
Anyone who wants to be a mole

238
00:11:18,220 --> 00:11:19,880
毫不犹豫地接受条件
accepts the first offer without question.

239
00:11:19,890 --> 00:11:21,380
他却讨价还价
He's negotiating.

240
00:11:21,850 --> 00:11:23,390
所以你相信他了
So you actually believe him?

241
00:11:25,710 --> 00:11:27,140
半信半疑
Not necessarily.

242
00:11:29,760 --> 00:11:32,630
但这不代表他没有价值
But that doesn't mean that he doesn't have value.

243
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:35,930
这些我们不需要了
Yeah, we're not gonna need any of these.

244
00:11:35,930 --> 00:11:37,350
全都放在这里
We're gonna keep these right here.

245
00:11:38,560 --> 00:11:40,580
凯特·鲍德温  久仰久仰
Kate Baldwin, the one and only.

246
00:11:40,580 --> 00:11:42,280
我就说听到这里有人
I thought I heard somebody in here.

247
00:11:42,440 --> 00:11:45,240
欢迎来白宫  或者应该说欢迎回白宫
Welcome to the White House. Or welcome back, I should say.

248
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:46,940
这里比我记忆中小
It feels smaller than I remember.

249
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:50,290
-他们安排你坐哪里  -这里  第二排
- Where do they have you sitting? - Right there, second row.

250
00:11:51,310 --> 00:11:53,510
我以为你会想要第一排
I would've thought you wanted first row.

251
00:11:53,640 --> 00:11:55,340
我听说你说话会飞吐沫
I heard you spit when you talk.

252
00:11:55,990 --> 00:11:57,850
明天总统会讲什么
What's the president speaking about tomorrow?

253
00:11:57,870 --> 00:11:59,840
-你真是不浪费一分一秒  -没错
- You don't waste a minute, do you? - No.

254
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:01,270
实不相瞒  我很惊讶
I gotta say, I was surprised

