00:12:01,270 --> 00:12:03,320
《电讯报》会派你来采访白宫
that the Telegraph sent you to cover the White House.

256
00:12:03,320 --> 00:12:05,000
谁会离开伦敦分社啊
I mean, who leaves the London bureau?

257
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:06,860
艾拉是我的爱徒
Ayla was a protégée of mine.

258
00:12:07,050 --> 00:12:09,680
明白了  他们把老师父都请来了
I see, so now they bring in the big guns.

259
00:12:09,770 --> 00:12:11,580
就一位师父  资历也够老
Just one gun, but big enough.

260
00:12:11,580 --> 00:12:14,390
-别打我的主意  -什么主意
- Don't get any ideas. - About what?

261
00:12:14,690 --> 00:12:16,460
这个记者证我不会摘的
This is gonna stay around my neck.

262
00:12:16,610 --> 00:12:18,700
你不能连续解雇两个《电讯报》的记者
You can't boot two reporters in a row from the Telegraph.

263
00:12:18,700 --> 00:12:21,910
-更不能是两个女记者  -我没这个意思
- Certainly not two women. - I have no desire to do that.

264
00:12:22,370 --> 00:12:24,030
跟你合作  我很荣幸
It's an honor to work with you.

265
00:12:24,030 --> 00:12:25,530
普利策奖  皮博迪奖
Pulitzer, Peabody.

266
00:12:25,530 --> 00:12:27,180
再拿个诺贝尔奖  就是三料冠军了
Get yourself a Nobel, you'll have a trifecta.

267
00:12:27,180 --> 00:12:28,760
你可真会说话
Oh, you're almost charming.

268
00:12:28,760 --> 00:12:30,620
凯特  我不是你的敌人
Kate, I'm not your enemy here.

269
00:12:30,620 --> 00:12:33,530
