You punished Ayla for doing good work.

270
00:12:33,730 --> 00:12:35,550
她发力  你反击  很公平
She hit hard and you hit back. Fair enough.

271
00:12:35,550 --> 00:12:37,930
我会加倍发力
Well, I'm gonna hit twice as hard as she ever did

272
00:12:37,930 --> 00:12:40,200
因为我可以  也应该这么做
because I can and because someone should.

273
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:41,740
放马过来吧
I look forward to it.

274
00:12:44,420 --> 00:12:48,110
你真不会说谎  我们明早见
You're such a terrible liar. I'll see you bright and early.

275
00:12:49,830 --> 00:12:51,030
有时间吗
You got a minute?

276
00:12:52,210 --> 00:12:53,040
有
Sure.

277
00:12:56,740 --> 00:12:59,330
这是明天声明的草稿
Here's the draft for the statement tomorrow.

278
00:12:59,550 --> 00:13:01,320
想让你斧正一下
I want it to be perfect.

279
00:13:01,360 --> 00:13:03,510
国会肯定会火力全开  回击我们
Congress will fire back, all guns blazing,

280
00:13:03,510 --> 00:13:06,350
邓巴也肯定会大作文章
and I'm sure Dunbar will make a meal and a half out of it.

281
00:13:06,350 --> 00:13:10,650
但我觉得准备进攻的感觉很好
But I gotta say, I feel good. To be on the offensive.

282
00:13:10,650 --> 00:13:12,580
如果不能私下东拼西凑出这些钱来
If I can't scrape the money together behind the scenes,

283
00:13:12,580 --> 00:13:15,360
我就光天化日之下抢银行
I'll rob the bank in broad goddamn daylight.

284
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:19,210
我们要强行逼迫他们通过《美国就业法案》
We'll cram America Works down their throats and watch them choke.

285
00:13:19,210 --> 00:13:20,980
不再谨小慎微
Enough tiptoeing.

286
00:13:22,740 --> 00:13:23,480
给
Here.

287
00:13:31,520 --> 00:13:33,370
这些改动很棒
Oh, these changes are good.

288
00:13:34,930 --> 00:13:37,110
看你这么兴奋  我也很高兴
It makes me happy to see you excited.

289
00:13:37,180 --> 00:13:39,090
我又能松口气了
I feel free again.

290
00:13:40,990 --> 00:13:43,440
-真希望我也能  -还在忙决议案吗
- I wish I felt the same. - The resolution?

