I should probably get some sleep.

298
00:14:09,110 --> 00:14:11,240
明天记得看新闻  会很有意思的
You watch the news tomorrow. Should be fun.

299
00:14:11,240 --> 00:14:14,060
-我会的  -晚安
- I will. - Good night.

