I've seen robberies and murders.

302
00:15:17,150 --> 00:15:18,990
见过毒品的瘟疫
I've seen the blight of drugs.

303
00:15:19,160 --> 00:15:20,440
我见过小孩子
I've seen little kids

304
00:15:20,440 --> 00:15:24,170
每天只能吃到从学校领到的那一顿饭
whose only meal each day was the one they get at school.

305
00:15:24,990 --> 00:15:26,510
知道这些事的根源是什么吗
You know what's at the root of all that?

306
00:15:26,870 --> 00:15:29,820
因为人们没有工作
Folks don't have jobs!

307
00:15:30,020 --> 00:15:33,460
华盛顿有六万失业人口
There are 60,000 unemployed people in Washington.

308
00:15:33,570 --> 00:15:35,120
这是场灾难
It's a disaster.

309
00:15:35,580 --> 00:15:38,260
更丢脸的是  这是国家的首都
And it's a disgrace here in the nation's capital.

310
00:15:38,730 --> 00:15:40,980
所以今早  在总统的敦促下
So this morning, at the president's urging,

311
00:15:40,980 --> 00:15:46,150
我宣布哥伦比亚特区进入紧急状态
I am declaring a state of emergency in the District of Columbia.

312
00:15:46,300 --> 00:15:49,460
