849
00:46:24,110 --> 00:46:25,950
钱是肯定不会少了你的
Well, I'll pay you well, and at the very least,

850
00:46:25,950 --> 00:46:28,360
这种活儿一向能捞一笔  是吧
this sort of access is worth its weight in gold, isn't it?

851
00:46:28,360 --> 00:46:29,600
先生  第一夫人回来了
Sir, the First Lady's back.

852
00:46:29,600 --> 00:46:32,230
我得在放焰火之前致辞
I have to go give my Fourth of July speech before the fireworks.

853
00:46:32,230 --> 00:46:35,110
-您要多久写完  -一月之前
